theme = ExtResource("3_6axw7")
text = "IN A WORLD OF TYRANNY, PLAGUED BY DARKNESS
AND CORPORATE OVERREACH, ONE HOMEY BEE
STOOD VALIANTLY ALONE AGAINST ALL ODDS.

HIS FELLOWS HAD FALLEN TO DRISMOL THE WISE,
ORANGE WIZARD OF THE EASTERN HIVE-BUT THIS
WOULD TURN OUT TO BE HIS UNDOING. . .





HOMEY BEE'S AAA ADVENTURE. . .



HAS JUST CONCLUDED!


DRISMOL'S WISDOM WAS NO MATCH FOR THE
SHEER POWER GAINED FROM OVER 700 HOURS
OF GRINDING MOLLARKS IN THE FIELDS OF
WOE. 

AFTER A HARD, LONG, HIGH QUALITY JOURNEY,
HOMEY BEE IS EXHAUSTED. HIS WINGS ARE SO
SORE!! ALL HE WANTS TO DO NOW. . .

IS TAKE A NAP. . .

LUCKILY, HE LIVES
AT THE VERY TOP
OF THE HIVE. . ."
horizontal_alignment = 1

